message.entry: The "{0}" operation is not supported. Try one of the supported operations: {1}.
Negative times are invalid. Use only positive inputs to create a valid time object.
The resulting time is outside of the valid time limits. The smallest valid time is (0:0) and the largest valid time is (4294967295:999999999).
The result of adding ({0}) to ({1}) is outside of the valid time limits. The smallest valid time is (0:0) and the largest valid time is (4294967295:999999999). Try adding a smaller value.
The result of subtracting ({0}) from ({1}) is outside of the valid time limits. The smallest valid time is (0:0) and the largest valid time is (4294967295:999999999). Try subtracting a smaller value.

The result of subtracting ({0}) from ({1}) is outside of the valid duration limits. The smallest valid duration is (-2147483648:0) and the largest valid duration is (2147483647:999999999). Try subtracting a smaller value.
